						<div class="postbody">Why such a complicated RAM-clearing routine?<br /><br />Adapted from the wiki:<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; &nbsp;ldx #0<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;txa $0<br /><br />@clrmem_top:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;sta $000, x<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;sta $100, x<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;; Reserving $200 for OAM display list, sta $200, x if you want<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;sta $300, x<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;sta $400, x<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;sta $500, x<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;sta $600, x<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;sta $700, x<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;inx<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;bne @clrmem_top<br /></div></div>

